    "body": "I think this is the same issue as https://github.com/pandas-dev/pandas/issues/17257. maybe also related to #16304. Welcome to have a look / PR to fix. These should be the same.\r\n\r\n```\r\nIn [13]: pd.merge(d1, d2, left_index=True, right_index=True, how='left')\r\nOut[13]: \r\n    v_x  v_y\r\nk           \r\nK0    1  4.0\r\nK0    1  5.0\r\nK1    2  NaN\r\nK2    3  NaN\r\n\r\nIn [14]: d1.join([d2], how='left')\r\nOut[14]: \r\n    v_x  v_y\r\nk           \r\nK0  1.0  4.0\r\nK0  1.0  5.0\r\nK1  2.0  NaN\r\nK2  3.0  NaN\r\nK3  NaN  6.0\r\n```"
